ow/pane scoping, evidence emission, and explicit actor-id override behavior\n\nLocal validation:\n- rustfmt --edition 2024 --check crates/frankenterm-core/src/policy.rs ✅\n- git diff --check -- crates/frankenterm-core/src/policy.rs ✅\n\nRCH/offloaded cargo attempts:\n- rch workers probe --all -> all 8 workers currently connection_failed (RCH-E100)\n- timeout 30s env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=target/rch-darkchapel-ft3681t62-check rch exec -- cargo check -p frankenterm-core --lib --tests --features mcp,mcp-client,web\n  - remote sync completed, remote execution failed (SSH connect failure to ubuntu@212.90.121.76), rch attempted fail-open local compile; outer timeout exited 124, so no compliant cargo proof recorded\n- timeout 30s env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=target/rch-darkchapel-ft3681t62-test rch exec -- cargo test -p frankenterm-core decision_context_from_input_records_identity_evidence -- --nocapture\n  - remote sync completed, remote execution failed (SSH connect failure to ubuntu@38.242.134.66), rch attempted fail-open local compile; outer timeout exited 124, so no compliant cargo proof recorded\n\nCoordination/infrastructure notes:\n- MCP Agent Mail registration/inbox fetch worked, but contact requests/file reservations failed repeatedly (database / transport errors), so I could not send the intended intro/reservation messages through mail during this slice.\n- policy.rs had concurrent unrelated edits land during this work; I kept this slice narrow and avoided broad formatter churn.","created_at":"2026-03-08T01:14:34Z"}]}
